title: Cyclones take on undefeated TCU
text:
Cyclones take on undefeated TCU Published 5:36 PM CDT Oct 17, 2015 A Large Text Photos 
The Iowa State Cyclones are going head-to-head against the undefeated TCU Horned Frogs at Jack Trice on Saturday. Other Stories 
TCU won its last trip to Ames 21-17 in 2013 and whipped the Cyclones 55-3 last year in Fort Worth.
